Bongo Flava&rsquo;s Diamond Platnumz has come out to reveal why he hasn&rsquo;t publicly posted a &lsquo;get-ell-soon message online for Zari Hassan&rsquo;s ex-husband Ivan Ssemwanga, who is bedridden.Ivan, who was rushed to a South African hospital last week over a coronary artery disease, has undergone various surgeries. Zari was by his side. A photo of Zari taking care of Ivan &ndash; with whom she has three kids together &ndash; went viral. This prompted the media to ask Diamond for his take.&ldquo;Watu wanashindwa kuelewa, Ivan anaumwa very serious...Situation iko very serious. Huyo ni mzazi mwenzake na ana kila haki ya kuhakikisha ameenda. Na mimi ndio mtu wa kwanza nikiamka nampigia simu &lsquo;Umeenda hospitali?&rsquo;&rdquo; Diamond told Clouds FM.&ldquo;Hebu imagine kesho na kesho kutwa asipoenda hata familia yangu itamuogopa itasema vipi Diamond akiumwa leo hii ataweza kuja? Lazima ionekane tofauti ili tutengeneze tamaduni tofauti katika maisha ya kawaida.&rdquo;On why he hasn&rsquo;t posted anything online, Diamond said, &ldquo;Swala lake la kuumwa liko very serious, alafu kulingana na situation ilivyotokea nyuma, unawezapost mtu na hujui atai-judge vipi. Wakati mwingine naambia Zari chochote kinafanyika ukienda kule, usiruhusu iende kwa mtandao kwa sababu unaweza ukatabiriwa vibaya.&rdquo;